### General API Tests

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### 1. Get API Schema
GET {{baseUrl}}/schema/

### 2. Get Swagger Documentation
GET {{baseUrl}}/docs/

### 3. Get ReDoc Documentation
GET {{baseUrl}}/redoc/

### 4. Health Check (if implemented)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/

### 5. Get API Version Info (if implemented)
GET {{baseUrl}}/version/

### 6. Test CORS (if needed)
OPTIONS {{baseUrl}}/auth/login/
Origin: http://localhost:3000
Access-Control-Request-Method: POST
Access-Control-Request-Headers: Content-Type

### 7. Test Rate Limiting (if implemented)
GET {{baseUrl}}/gym/gyms/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Test Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/gym/gyms/?page=1&page_size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Test Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/gym/gyms/?search=test
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Test Filtering
GET {{baseUrl}}/gym/gyms/?created_after=2024-01-01
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Test Sorting
GET {{baseUrl}}/gym/gyms/?ordering=-created_at
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Test Error Handling - Invalid Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/gym/gyms/
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token

### 13. Test Error Handling - Missing Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/gym/gyms/

### 14. Test Error Handling - Invalid Data
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phone": "invalid_phone",
    "password": ""
}

### 15. Test Error Handling - Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/gym/gyms/99999/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
